## Supported Languages

| Language | Extensions |
|----------|------------|
| Python | .py |
| C | .c, .h |
| C++ | .cpp, .cc, .hpp |
| C# | .cs |
| Java | .java |
| JavaScript | .js, .jsx |
| TypeScript | .ts, .tsx |
| Go | .go |
| Rust | .rs |
| Bash | .sh, .bash |

